SnapChat these days

SnapChat's advent brought a big sea change into the world of social media. Rather than the traditional format of posting photos that is a social norm, now on SnapChat the prime focus lies in the type of experience that can be created through images. One user manually set the timer and posed, while another can quickly focus, hold the image and shake their device to imitate the theatrical effect.

The Counselor and the Future of Classical Music — An Interview

The Celtic Harp Trio, led by Rachel, consists of three musicians: Tikko (violin) and Julianna Allison (flute), along with Rachel on Celtic harp. This not only extends our enjoyment of the music, but their titles add, sometimes unexpectedly, even more substance to their already compelling compositions. Julianna DD Allison’s flute begins the short march-like Prelude, as she echoes the harp’s tune on the halfway mark. The first of the three distinct main movements begins in the almost jangling Celtic harp, with a bustling rhythm and a prominent flutist. This time, the piece begins solemnly on flute and harp recalling the dirge-like opening Prelude, only this time the flautist rings out with a vivid burst of higher notes, and then leads to a darker and richer harp part with extended double-harmonics. Reyes was as irrepressible a character as his counterpart Gutierrez, with a great sense of humor.
